OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FNI Water will soon submit a new
OL,7,Fbusiness plan to the Utility
OL,8,FRegulator. It's for a five-year period
OL,9,Fbeginning in 2028, and have revealed
OL,10,Fto UTV their estimation of how much
OL,11,Ffunding is required.
OL,13,FIt's an eye-watering figure.
OL,15,FDr Gary Curran, Director of
OL,16,FEngineering, NI Water, said that "it's
OL,17,Fin the order for this first five year
OL,18,Fperiod of three and a half billion
OL,19,Fpounds of capital investment."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
