PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FThat's to reverse decades of
OL,7,Funderfunding.
OL,9,FWater infrastructure is in a state of
OL,10,Fdecay, even turning NI Water into a
OL,11,Fpolluter in some places.
OL,13,FBut it's protected from public
OL,14,Fprosecution.
OL,16,FToday, the Environment Minister said
OL,17,Fthat must change.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
