FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FAndrew Muir MLA, Environment Minister
OL,7,Fsaid: "For my department to deliver
OL,8,Fits statutory duties and respond
OL,9,Feffectively to present water quality
OL,10,Fchallenges.
OL,12,F"It needs to ensure that regulation is
OL,13,Fdelivered in compliance with the law
OL,14,Fand effective enforcement is applied
OL,15,Fconsistently across all sectors that
OL,16,Fcause pollution."
OL,18,FNI Water has previously warned paying
OL,19,Ffines will reduce funding for
OL,20,Fdevelopment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
