OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FA new #7 million pumping station under
OL,7,Fis currently under construction in
OL,8,FDerry.
OL,10,FThis is much, much more than just a
OL,11,Fgiant hole in the ground. This is key
OL,12,Fto unlocking development potential.
OL,14,FIt will allow for the construction of
OL,15,Fup to 1,500 homes in this part of the
OL,16,Fcity. But it isn't happening enough in
OL,17,Fother places, says the construction
OL,18,Findustry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
