PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FThe sector blames an inadequate sewage
OL,7,Fnetwork for putting the brakes on the
OL,8,Fbuilding of homes. They're going to
OL,9,Fask for #3.5 billion.
OL,11,FPaul McErlean, Build Homes NI said:
OL,12,F"That is what is required to build a
OL,13,Fmodern sewage system that'll supply
OL,14,Fthe houses."
OL,16,FWhen asked whether he had any
OL,17,Fconfidence that that funding will be
OL,18,Fmet, he said "zero at the moment."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FUltimately, Stormont's Department for
OL,7,FInfrastructure will be asked to find
OL,8,Fthe money.
OL,10,FBut the Minister says #3.5 billion is
OL,11,Fmore than the budget for her entire
OL,12,Fdepartment and she insists Northern
OL,13,FIreland should remain the only part of
OL,14,Fthe UK that doesn't pay domestic water
OL,15,Fcharges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
