FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773045643
OL,3,CAround #3.5bn needed by NI Water to
OL,4,Cdevelop waste-water system
OL,6,FLiz Kimmins MLA, Infrastructure
OL,7,FMinister said: "It's a good headline
OL,8,Fat this point to say, "Oh, we don't
OL,9,Fhave enough money to deliver what NI
OL,10,FWater says is needed," but we have to
OL,11,Flook at that as a department and
OL,12,Fassess it and see what's actually
OL,13,Frealistic and what we can do. But we
OL,14,Fdo that in partnership."
OL,16,FParts of the wastewater network date
OL,17,Fback to the Victorian era, but funding
OL,18,Fis the blockage that's prevented the
OL,19,Fsystem from so far fully entering the
OL,20,F21st century.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
